Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:57.82,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(645,545)\fad(526,0)}CASA DE KYROS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês estiveram juntos no Exército Revolucionário?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin, não o acorde.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Só vim vê-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Já vai embora do país?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque uns caras chatos voltaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,O CP-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,São caras que participaram\N do esquema de Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós somos o alvo deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Em um ou dois dias, Dressrosa \Nvai estar cheia de gente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês também deveriam ir embora o quanto antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por nos avisar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sabia que havia outro\N irmão além de Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que ouço isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro que sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy deve ter sido o que ficou mais surpreso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Por muito tempo, eles pensaram que eu estava morto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando éramos crianças, eu sempre\N estava junto com Luffy e Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:38.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Sempre nos metíamos em problemas,\N o velho Garp nos treinava...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,E nós queríamos ser piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Bebemos juntos e nos\N tornamos irmãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas um dia me envolvi em um acidente.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,954)}Não, não foi um acidente.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Algo está errado com esta cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Todos estão loucos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:23.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Eles sabem que muitas pessoas vão morrer,\N mas agem normalmente e até sorriem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não quero ficar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Tenho que avisá-los o quanto antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.05,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo, garoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:57.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Esta cidade cheira muito pior que o Terminal Cinza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:01.41,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Cheira a gente podre por dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,E eu sei que aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:08.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...nunca serei livre!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:18.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:24.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Estou com muita vontade de vê-los...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Aqui me sinto como um pássaro enjaulado...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:34.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não acho que vou aguentar muito neste país \Nonde as pessoas estão podres por dentro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O que é liberdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Onde ela está?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.34,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.44,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:05.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Alguém me ajude...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Socorro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.36,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Por que demorou tanto, Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.26,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A espera estava ficando eterna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você...! O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,É horrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.30,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Precisamos cuidar dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.16,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,É uma emergência!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.96,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Chamem o médico de bordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.18,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele acordou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não o assuste, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não era minha intenção fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Que falta de respeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:01.81,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Onde estou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você está no nosso navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.38,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Nas suas coisas está escrito Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.33,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Esse é o seu nome?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.13,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Então, como você se chama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.67,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não sei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.05,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Será que ele...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:28.92,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:34.80,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele não se lembra de nada?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.70,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não, nem mesmo do próprio nome...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:42.79,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Conheci esse garoto pela primeira vez no Bairro Alto do Reino de Goa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:46.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida de que ele é um nobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.54,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Então, vamos levá-lo para lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:49.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vamos procurar seus pais...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.67,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.27,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não quero voltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.82,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.25,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:04.17,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...é a última coisa que eu quero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, você não se lembrava \Nde nada até dois anos atrás?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você conseguiu recuperar suas\N memórias sendo algo tão grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Graças ao Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,É o que eu acho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi no pior momento,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.57,Main,,0,0,0,,mas foi exatamente isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...que me fez lembrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.10,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(639,480)\fad(274,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}BALTIGO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.10,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,715)\fad(274,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}QUARTEL-GENERAL DO EXÉRCITO REVOLUCIONÁRIO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.69,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Está muito barulhento.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Oh, chefe do gabinete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Chegou na hora certa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Venha conosco para a sala\N do conselho de guerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:01.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A Grande Guerra entre a Marinha e os\N Piratas de Barba Branca chegou ao fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.02,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Barba Branca perdeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.02,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,E o Iva-san?{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não diz que ele morreu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.05,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quem morreu na guerra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.95,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...foi Barba Branca, um dos Yonkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.45,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,e...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...Ace, o Punho de Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Além disso, olhe isso, Dragon-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.34,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,É verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Luffy, o Chapéu de Palha, é seu filho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.54,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.36,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.36,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.70,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vou ser um pirata,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:10.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,vou derrotar todos e ser o mais famoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.65,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Isso será prova suficiente de que um dia eu vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.65,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo-kun, o que aconteceu?{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você está agindo estranho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.05,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vocês sabiam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:58.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Dizem que Akainu perfurou\N o corpo de Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:08.39,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(194,0)}Aparentemente, se bebemos juntos,\N nos tornamos irmãos.{\i1}{\i0}{Como exemplo do mostrado por Ryu no 736, isso deveria ir assim no início.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.27,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não importa onde estejamos ou o que façamos, nossos laços nunca se romperão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Então, a partir de hoje, seremos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.91,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...irmãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,993)}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.20,Secondary,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,993)}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:52.77,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo-kun!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:53.72,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não foi um pirata desconhecido que morreu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:11.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Não era uma ameaça da Era da Pirataria que precisava ser eliminada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...é meu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,...irmão.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.26,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não vou fugir de ninguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,988)}Nem perder para ninguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.02,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O chefe acordou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:47.96,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:50.22,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Que alívio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Achei que você ia morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo-kun!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:06.18,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você teve uma febre terrível, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.65,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você não acordou por três dias.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:12.22,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu estava preocupada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.68,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você recuperou a memória?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.94,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu me lembro de tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:30.72,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quem eu sou, por que deixei minha casa e fui para o mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.58,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.80,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Que bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.30,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você vai deixar o Exército Revolucionário?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.66,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não, não vou deixar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O Dragon-san ainda está aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:49.76,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:55.38,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2439)}Preciso contar uma coisa para ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:12.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Naquele momento, senti que Ace me disse:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,"Você é Sabo, meu irmão e irmão de Luffy".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Finalmente pude vir aqui, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.70,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Olha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:51.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Luffy continua avançando em seu caminho para se tornar o rei dos piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:55.58,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar do nosso irmão.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.92,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quero pedir um favor a todos do Exército Revolucionário.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.90,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Há uma Akuma no Mi que quero conseguir, custe o que custar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.74,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mas, Luffy-senpai, e a Mera Mera no Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:27.50,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,395)}{\pos(640,715)\fad(250,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.54,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Há pessoas para quem não quero dar, mas não tenho escolha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.55,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A vida dos meus companheiros é insubstituível.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.97,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vou conseguir a Mera Mera no Mi, custe o que custar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:43.55,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Então não se preocupe e vá!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.30,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Entendi, obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.39,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar você conseguir a Mera Mera no Mi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.84,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:07.16,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não fale de forma tão informal com Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:12.54,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele é o irmão mais novo do lendário pirata, Punho de Fogo Ace-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:16.62,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,e o futuro Rei dos Piratas, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.51,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que há com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.73,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você aparece do nada e diz que não posso ter a Mera Mera no Mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.44,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sou eu, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.44,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Como assim é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.30,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Escuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.80,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A Mera Mera é uma lembrança de Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.94,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se você a quiser, é meu inimigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Além disso, você me chamou de Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.49,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,mas olha para esta barba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:03.73,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você achou que não reconheceria o rosto do meu irmão mais novo só porque está disfarçado?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.41,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Irmão mais novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:08.15,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Escuta, os únicos que podem me chamar de irmão...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.46,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...são o falecido Ace e...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...alguém que morreu muito antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.66,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:43.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Roubamos uma garrafa de licor de Dadan e bebemos juntos...{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.56,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que diabos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.56,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Onde diabos você estava?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.58,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que você tinha morrido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.28,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.54,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Estou feliz que você ainda esteja vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:26.72,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mas, Sabo, eu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:30.33,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Deixei que matassem Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.28,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:35.74,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ace morreu, mas pelo menos...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.59,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...estou feliz que você tenha sobrevivido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:42.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu quase perdi meus dois irmãos sem poder fazer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:48.14,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se você tivesse morrido, eu teria ficado sozinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.43,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.67,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por continuar vivo, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.93,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Posso comer a Mera Mera no Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim.{Não acho que essa linha será permitida}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.78,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Isso seria ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:34.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Claro!{\fad(0,1948)}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy está sorrindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,O que ele estará sonhando?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, vou indo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Já?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Já vi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,E fiz uma Vivre Card de Luffy por precaução.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, em que momento?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou pegar uma parte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Pode ser que Luffy seja incontrolável,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,mas cuidem dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Conte conosco!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Disse o mesmo que Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sou Hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, acabei de sair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Já volto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Como foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun...{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que ele desligou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é um arrogante!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuidado, Hack-san!{\i1}{\i0}{Não acho que deva separar isso}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Podemos partir a qualquer momento?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, a qualquer momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando voltarmos para Baltigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,não vou parar de contar ao Dragon-san sobre Luffy!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.16,Main,,0,0,0,,De verdade,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.22,Main,,0,0,0,,estou feliz por ter te visto de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos apressar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.90,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(665,375)\fad(250,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Em que ele caiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Você poderia ver?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele caiu em um.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Decidimos que o "um" seria do Chapéu de Palha,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.15,Main,,0,0,0,,não foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, ele venceu este duelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vamos prendê-lo esta noite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas decidir com um dado, Issho-san...?{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:22:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Procuramos por todo o país e finalmente descobrimos sua localização!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Você discutiu tanto com o Almirante da Frota Sakazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ele quer as cabeças de Law e do Chapéu de Palha, esta é sua chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Maynard-san!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizer tudo isso depois que o dado foi lançado...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é patético.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:23.23,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(499,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém viu Lucy depois disso?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, ninguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos quero agradecê-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Há tumulto por toda parte.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sejam piratas ou criminosos,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,não há dúvida de que são nossos salvadores.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Vovô!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Nem meu pai nem Lucy estão no palácio!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Kyros me ligou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles estão juntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Por falar nisso...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu voltar ao trono,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:15.41,Main,,0,0,0,,você seria a princesa, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:23.00,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,385)\fad(250,250)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}DIA SEGUINTE\NNOVO MUNDO - SUNNY\N(TRIPULAÇÃO DO CHAPÉU DE PALHA)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Depois do esforço que foi para fugir do navio da Big Mom...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:41.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que vocês se metem em problemas de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:45.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tem jeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Se apresse!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,É para o bem deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se metam onde não foram chamados!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Deveríamos ter ficado esperando no navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que diabos vocês se adiantam e entram aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca e faça o que eu digo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:01.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Você vai fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ou quer que eu esmague seu coração?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas você vai pagar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Fizemos bem em desembarcar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda podemos salvá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos do seu poder!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.22,0:24:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, por que não me tratam com mais gentileza?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Você disse algo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Parem de mostrar isso o tempo todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Depressa, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.85,0:24:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me dêem ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:35.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito guaxinim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.52,0:24:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou uma rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas são idênticos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Se apresse!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.96,0:24:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eles morrerem, não vou perdoar você!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.09,0:24:54.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos do seu poder!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,É difícil correr neste lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.48,0:25:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que nos separamos de Sanji-san e dos outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.90,0:25:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos com problemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.39,0:25:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Demos muita atenção àquela garota misteriosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.92,0:25:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.68,0:25:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Primeiro eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.68,0:25:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.68,0:25:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, que cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.66,0:25:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Que cruel, que cruel!{Dejo sin separar esto}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.96,0:25:32.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Onami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.76,0:25:34.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Estão nos perseguindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.57,0:25:58.82,Main,,0,0,0,,É só isso, intrusos?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.82,0:26:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.22,0:26:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Para onde foi aquela mulher?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.28,0:26:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que entraram nesta ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.41,0:26:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Respondam!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.26,0:26:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Este é um lugar peculiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.52,0:26:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.76,0:26:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.92,0:26:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Vai haver uma lluviarupção!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,De novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.66,0:26:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Protejam-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.30,0:26:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.23,0:26:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Chuva?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:34.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma grande quantidade de água?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.88,0:26:39.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Aconteça o que acontecer, eu vou protegê-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.28,0:26:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.18,0:26:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.28,0:26:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.75,0:26:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Me ajudem!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.22,0:27:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.05,0:27:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.91,0:27:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Que dor de cabeça dão os usuários de Akuma no Mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.76,0:27:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe por não ter conseguido protegê-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vão escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Malditos invasores!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.40,0:27:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.24,0:27:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Resistam!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.50,0:27:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, como sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.44,0:27:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.20,0:27:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Agradeço.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.68,0:27:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Se vir um suspeito,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.90,0:27:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,mate-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.73,0:27:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.09,0:27:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhor ossos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.14,0:27:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Finalmente consegui protegê-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.10,0:28:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe o resto comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.32,0:28:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Que arrogante!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.21,0:28:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Chifre de Ovelha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.33,0:28:10.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.70,0:28:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,E esses braços?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.66,0:28:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhor ossos!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.52,0:28:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Tome isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.08,0:28:18.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Desfile das Almas!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.68,0:28:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Senhor ossos, isso foi incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.94,0:28:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é essa habilidade?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.08,0:28:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.30,0:28:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Mantenha essa posição.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.10,0:28:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.82,0:28:40.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Diable: Mouton...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.84,0:28:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,...Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.42,0:28:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Sheepshead-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.41,0:29:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.48,0:29:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem são vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.93,0:29:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem são vocês, desgraçados?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.06,0:29:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Que desagradável!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.42,0:29:14.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Gin Rummy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.96,0:29:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Garotos!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.24,0:29:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Retirada!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.62,0:29:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram Sheepshead-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.62,0:29:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.62,0:29:20.53,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.53,0:29:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ainda não encontramos o samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.13,0:29:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós os encurralamos até aqui,\Ne ele ainda não apareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.78,0:29:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,O samurai não está aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.58,0:29:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Informem a ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.98,0:29:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.98,0:29:29.73,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.92,0:29:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,A água está indo embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.98,0:29:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,O que será que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.16,0:29:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma ilha estranha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:46.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Espero que aquela garota esteja bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.15,0:29:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela é mais rápida que nós, estará bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.18,0:29:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.82,0:30:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.65,0:30:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Venham aqui rápido, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.72,0:30:06.32,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Chopperemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.32,0:30:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Está na floresta lá embaixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.96,0:30:08.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.64,0:30:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma corrida contra o tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.24,0:30:20.89,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(244,237)}ESCONDERIJO DOS PIRATAS KID
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.18,0:30:32.43,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.56,0:30:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.56,0:30:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.24,0:30:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem um buraco enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.74,0:30:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Um buraco?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Algo caiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.82,0:30:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Peguem suas armas!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.59,0:30:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.59,0:30:49.74,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.88,0:30:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,É isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.51,0:31:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sem dúvida é enorme.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.34,0:31:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,De onde caiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.25,0:31:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos fez isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.00,0:31:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, tem forma humana, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.88,0:31:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.61,0:31:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Havia uma lenda que dizia que \Nno céu desses lugares...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.76,0:31:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...havia uma ilha do céu onde \Nhabitava um monstro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.40,0:31:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Você quer dizer que alguém o \Njogou da ilha do céu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.16,0:31:38.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Capitão Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.32,0:31:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,O impacto fez um dos nossos \Nbarcos virar!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.45,0:31:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você disse?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.86,0:31:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Zombando de nós...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.40,0:31:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.48,0:31:52.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Os fortes vivem e os fracos morrem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.36,0:31:56.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1447)}Este mundo é assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.48,0:32:01.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alguns minutos antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.30,0:32:07.80,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(488,0)}ILHA DO CÉU - RUÍNAS DO TERMINAL BALLOON
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.80,0:32:17.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que ele está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.06,0:32:19.29,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Deixe ele fazer o que quiser, monge!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.29,0:32:20.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Esse cara é louco!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.98,0:32:24.27,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Estamos no céu, \Na dez mil metros de altura.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.27,0:32:28.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,O homem procurava um lugar para morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.96,0:32:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ele está falando sério, por que pará-lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.00,0:32:35.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Esse homem,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.46,0:32:39.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,como pirata, foi derrotado sete vezes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.47,0:32:44.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...e foi capturado dezoito vezes pela Marinha e por navios inimigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.56,0:32:51.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ele viveu como um criminoso, \Nsofrendo tortura após tortura.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.76,0:33:03.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Agora ele está tentando se suicidar...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.86,0:33:06.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...de uma maneira estranha,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.32,0:33:09.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,pulando de uma ilha do céu.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.40,0:33:16.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,E agora voltamos ao presente.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.76,0:33:20.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Vou repetir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.96,0:33:24.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ele sozinho desafiou a Marinha e os Yonkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.10,0:33:28.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,foi capturado dezoito vezes e \Nsentenciado à morte quarenta vezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.16,0:33:33.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Quando ia ser enforcado, \Nas correntes se quebraram.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.84,0:33:37.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Quando foi enviado para a guilhotina, ela quebrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:41.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Quando ia ser perfurado por \Nlanças, elas se quebraram.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.09,0:33:47.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Como resultado, ele afundou \Nnove navios prisão.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.56,0:33:51.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,965)}Ou seja, ninguém conseguiu matá-lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.80,0:33:55.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...nem ele mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.68,0:34:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,E esse monstro?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.58,0:34:24.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.24,0:34:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Minha cabeça dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.72,0:34:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Não consegui morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.04,0:34:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Mais uma vez sobrevivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.48,0:34:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele conseguiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.16,0:34:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...o velho Barba Branca.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:59.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,O homem que procurava \Num lugar para morrer...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:02.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...é Kaidou, o Rei das Feras.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.94,0:35:11.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No um contra um, Kaidou sempre vence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.02,0:35:14.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,É o que dizem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.02,0:35:19.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ele é o pirata conhecido como \Na criatura mais poderosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.96,0:35:24.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...entre os seres vivos do ar, mar e terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.42,0:35:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho escolha, tenho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.10,0:35:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.60,0:35:49.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Depressa, Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.91,0:35:54.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Termine os preparativos para a batalha final!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.78,0:36:01.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me importo se acabarmos \Ndestruindo este mundo chato!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.18,0:36:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Que comece a maior guerra \Nque este mundo já viu!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.47,0:36:09.50,OP11 Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,10)}Tradução: Juan Tlgd\NRevisão: RAFAEL
